Description: MiniCluster - Lightweight Application Orchestration Platform
 MiniCluster is a lightweight application orchestration and management
 platform that provides a web-based control center for managing
 distributed applications, services, and configurations.
 .
 Features:
  - Web-based dashboard for application management
  - Real-time service monitoring and metrics
  - Process lifecycle management
  - Configuration management with variable resolution
  - Multi-machine support
